Q. Show the application generator
A. rails generate

Q. How to use rails helper methods
A.   
   1. ActionController::Base.helpers.number_to_currency(12)
   2. ActionView::Base.new.number_to_currency(12)
   3. class A
        include ActionView::Helpers
      end

      A.new.number_to_currency(12)

Q. how to fix uninitialized constant ActiveSupport::Dependencies::Mutex error
A. rvm 1.8.7 gem install rubygems-update -v='1.4.2'
   update_rubygems

Q.create logger multiple  file 
A.  config.logger = Logger.new("#{RAILS_ROOT}/log/#{ENV['RAILS_ENV']}.log", 100, 200 * 1024  * 1024) 

Q. How to set rvm ruby with gemset
A. rvm use 1.8.7@rails3 --default

Q. Rvm install on ubuntu machine
A. 1. sudo apt-get install libmagick9-dev ruby1.8-dev
   2. sudo gem install rmagick

Q. How to compile sass and coffescript
A. rake assets:precompile
